{"tid":1019602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲就愛上她！21歲女和「喪屍」結婚　還找8喪屍當伴娘伴郎","createTime":"2019-02-13T05:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T09:44:43.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"05fd654efdd6745eb414e91e514a081a1eceec45","tid":1019602,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3892/d3892853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3892%2Fd3892853.jpg&h=e61f25cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女子選擇和交往5年的喪屍娃娃結婚。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／Felicity Kadlec Rossi）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國麻薩諸塞州一名21歲女子竟然和交往5年的「喪屍」結婚，還花了500美元（約台幣1.5萬元）盛大舉行婚禮，而婚禮的賓客也很特別，除了有女子的4名親屬到場，還有8名「喪屍」朋友擔任她的伴娘伴郎。<br />\n21歲女子卡德萊克(Felicity Kadlec)13歲開始蒐集外表恐怖的喪屍娃娃，父親當時將喪屍娃娃凱莉(Kelly)當成禮物送她，原本她對凱莉並沒有特殊感情，直到16歲時才突然發現自己愛上了對方，「當爸爸去世後，我常常會向凱莉尋求安慰，導致我們變得愈來愈親密，因為她是爸爸為我買的人。」<br />\n卡德萊克選擇在去年9月和凱莉盛大完成婚禮，她穿著白色婚紗，凱莉則是穿上黑色燕尾服，現場還有8名她的喪屍玩偶充當伴娘伴郎，以及4名親友一起見證，她們的愛情雖然無法獲得大眾的理解，但她仍義無反顧，「當我對我們的感情愈來愈有自信，我知道我必須嫁給她」。<br />\n卡德萊克說，凱莉在她眼中是37歲的喪屍娃娃，即使對方擁有喪屍般的外表也完全不介意，「我接受凱莉所有的一切，我看著她血淋淋的臉，不介意她沒有下巴，只想和她度過餘生。」<br />\n▼卡德萊克時常在臉書上和凱莉放閃。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／Felicity Kadlec Rossi）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3892/d3892855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3892%2Fd3892855.jpg&h=20702c48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190213/1376909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190213%2F1376909.htm&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=db046c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190213/1376909.htm</a>"},{"pid":"98dcb9ba1efe52063b10621ecd2ee052a9568fb5","tid":1019602,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1016309aa0ceda4be23475cdfb80b5e03f3655","tid":1019602,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ad255697762e2dfd96c5af04737eac09de7d62","tid":1019602,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:09:55.000Z","msg":"撞邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6133537602eba174b51a5949dd6ba240a8b2a5","tid":1019602,"uid":221055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"個老豆送啲咁嘅公仔比個13歲嘅女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f559a30496b9678c734a6faab77c6d1494a65f","tid":1019602,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"女？"},{"pid":"7226d4c7cc11436b0447618273b794d41af97e1e","tid":1019602,"uid":32282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"女子?"},{"pid":"9c4af1d5ba8423e245bd7b79d0ceb15121d17849","tid":1019602,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"係咪娃鬼新娘現實版"},{"pid":"ea2d068b7d94abe1be50b30030a05a8256cea12b","tid":1019602,"uid":59526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"條女仲恐怖過隻喪屍"},{"pid":"97264ced225d38d9b2e32a623763204ab2af4adf","tid":1019602,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be9914cb465e1a2a5800a45c403d9a44f94898db","tid":1019602,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"佢係咪想隻喪屍咬鳩佢，幫佢減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d81067b544fa154895eac481f79b8cc346bfda","tid":1019602,"uid":99941,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-1